 
<p>
A billion personal data records from Chinese national <a href="/glossary.html#thug">thugs</a> were
<a href="https://techcrunch.com/2022/07/07/china-leak-police-database/">taken by crackers and sold</a>.
<p>
Forget about "data protection"!  Our safety depends on <a href="https://gnu.org/philosophy/surveillance-vs-democracy.html">prohibiting
the systems that collect data</a>.

 